These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: plum, mango
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, ship
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
2. the person eating plum is not to the right of the person driving the ship##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | plum   | mango   |
| Transport   | ship | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, water
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | water | sprite   |
| Sport      | weightlifting | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: apple, tomato
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, reggae
1. the person eating apple is not to the left of the fan of reggae##8
2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | tomato | apple |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | reggae     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
There 2 different types of food: corn, apricot
2 different pets are kept: turtle, hedgehog
1. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the person eating corn##8
2. the person eating corn is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |
| Food   | apricot | corn |
| Pet    | turtle    | hedgehog |

